(d) No allowance shall be made on account of any improvements effected or works constructed after the publication of the notice to yield up possession;
No allowance shall be made on account of any improvements effected or works constructed after the publication of the notice to yield up possession;
(e) Where part only of the land held by any person is acquired, there shall be taken into account any probable enhancement of the value of the residue of the land by reason of the proximity of any improvements or works made or constructed or to be made or constructed on the part acquired;
